ISLAMABAD, May 27 (APP): Prime Minister Shehbaz Sharif on Monday held a telephonic conversation with Acting President Syed Yusuf Raza Gilani to extend congratulations on his son Ali Qasim Gilani’s historic win in the by-elections from constituency 148.
The acting president thanked the prime minister and expressed best wishes for him, a President House press release said.
